### 測試 Theater API Enum 驗證

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5041
@token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### 1. ✅ 測試正確的 Theater Type - Digital
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/theaters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試數位廳",
  "type": "Digital",
  "floor": 3,
  "rowCount": 2,
  "columnCount": 3,
  "seats": [
    ["Standard", "Aisle", "Standard"],
    ["Wheelchair", "Aisle", "Standard"]
  ]
}

